RTRS - Normandy details gold hedge position . Normandy Mining Ltd said on Wednesday its gold hedge position totalled 5 . 9 million ounces at an average deliverable price of A $ 595 per ounce realised at September 30 , compared to the average spot price of A $ 514 . " This compares very favourably with the recent spot price of gold of A $ 481 per ounce and reinforces the wisdom of the company ' s conservative stance with respect to gold hedging , " Normandy said in its September quarter production report . At June 30 , Normandy had 6 . 26 million ounces of gold hedged at an average price of A $ 719 per ounce . - - Sydney newsroom 61 - 2 9373 - 1800 
